00:00:03:210000.Speaker: Steph

00:00:24:010000.Speaker: Sheldon

00:00:35:110000.Speaker: Sheldon

00:00:41:210000.Speaker: Steph

00:00:57:000000.Speaker: Sheldon

00:01:02:080000.Speaker: Leonard
00:01:02:080000.Dialogue: Do you understand that Stephanie's not here to treat your imaginary ailments?

00:01:06:150000.Dialogue: How is it imaginary that I keep hearing an octave above Middle C? Is that imaginary?

00:01:33:030000.Speaker: Sheldon
00:01:33:030000.Dialogue: I'd like to begin the meeting by congratulating you on the progress in your relationship with Dr. Stephanie.

00:02:12:080000.Speaker: Leonard
00:02:12:080000.Dialogue: Wait, I only initialed it because I never thought it would happen!

00:02:17:080000.Speaker: Leonard

00:02:26:100000.Speaker: Sheldon
00:02:26:100000.Dialogue: Now, to review, the following provisions are hereby activated: In the refrigerator, as opposed to us having two separate shelves and one communal shelf, the three of us now get individual shelves and the door becomes communal.

00:02:37:050000.Speaker: Sheldon

00:02:44:010000.Speaker: Sheldon

00:02:55:170000.Speaker: Sheldon
00:02:55:170000.Dialogue: At least take this with you. And have Stephanie initial here, here, here, here...

00:03:25:100000.Speaker: Sheldon
